{"tid":1798374,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MBC咁撚大膽唔侵BITHIT","createTime":"2019-12-26T07:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T10:57:18.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7425d2bb5ccc704886ad895eaeb7a3f98700a2d4","tid":1798374,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"Big Hit收購GFRIEND所屬公司 MBC出演告吹<br />\n<br />\nGFRIEND作為BIG HIT旗下Source Music的招牌女子組合備受喜愛，《2019 MBC歌謠大祭典》的出演告吹。<br />\n<br />\nMBC最近公開了&quot;2019MBC歌謠大祭典&quot;的出演者。 但是相關陣容中沒有GFRIEND的名字，讓很多粉絲們感到遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n2015年出道的GFRIEND在之前發表的每張專輯都席捲榜單和音樂放送ㄧ位，聚集了超高人<br />\n氣。今年1月14日發行正規2輯、7月1日發行迷你7輯的GFRIEND，在MBC《SHOW! 音樂中心》三次獲得第一名。<br />\n<br />\n特別是GFRIEND在1月發表的正規2輯主打歌成爲2019年音樂放送的首個大滿貫主人公之後，7月以迷你7輯主打歌《Fever》成為今年最活躍的2個大滿貫。<br />\n<br />\nBTS唔去BIGHIT旗下全部冇得上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b450a82beb199e228404fc1f73383f301197293","tid":1798374,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"儘管如此GFRIEND卻和Big Hit新人組合TXT一起沒能進入&quot;2019MBC歌謠大祭典&quot;的陣容。<br />\n雖然會出演《2019 SBS歌謠大戰》和《2019 KBS歌謠大慶典》,但是不出演《2019 MBC歌謠大祭典》多少有些疑問。<br />\n<br />\n對此，OSEN的採訪結果顯示，BIG HIT收購的SOURCE MUSIC所屬的GFRIEND以與防彈少年團沒有區別爲由,受到了MBC的不利待遇。 <br />\n防彈少年團因為海外日程不能參加&quot;2019MBC歌謠大祭典&quot;,對GFRIEND產生了負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n某歌謠界相關人士對OSEN表示:&quot;從電視臺的立場來看，防彈少年團邀請是最重要的,這是大家都知道的事實。 <br />\n但是，利用這些方法產生其他受害者是不正確的。 現在已經不是電視臺以藝人出演為條件的年代了。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n31日,防彈少年團將參加在美國紐約時代廣場舉行的ABC電視臺新年前夜特輯節目，因此不參加&quot;2019MBC歌謠大祭典&quot;是日程上不可避免的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n但是MBC方面受到了根據防彈少年團的出演與否，在年末舞臺等音樂節目中限制同一所屬公司歌手出演的嫌疑。 MBC的這種措施被認爲是公營電視臺的蠻橫行爲，預計很多K-POP粉絲和觀眾會感到失望。<br />\n<br />\n另外，OSEN無法聯繫到MBC。<br />\n== == == == == == == == == ==<br />\n<br />\n女友從2015出道後每年都有參與歌謠大祭典"},{"pid":"29549e89d84195e3d01063ad6bbaa813e9fcb6c3","tid":1798374,"uid":48577,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"究竟Bts有冇食過GF"},{"pid":"4708a4dcd058d7ca4a8df500ef59b1227c46414f","tid":1798374,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"29549e89d84195e3d01063ad6bbaa813e9fcb6c3","tid":1798374,"uid":48577,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"究竟Bts有冇食過GF"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:57:04.000Z","msg":"Bts冇咁重口味 佢哋話個鍾意red velvet <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b661c14f1210d0d3fd7ea3c5653eae00a8eb13b0","tid":1798374,"uid":256952,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4708a4dcd058d7ca4a8df500ef59b1227c46414f","tid":1798374,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"29549e89d84195e3d01063ad6bbaa813e9fcb6c3","tid":1798374,"uid":48577,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"究竟Bts有冇食過GF"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:57:04.000Z","msg":"Bts冇咁重口味 佢哋話個鍾意red velvet <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:57:18.000Z","msg":"狗朋友行埋一邊啦"}]}